[The Lipetskaya Oblast is a federal subject of Russia. Its administrative centre is the city of Lipetsk. Population: 1 172 818 (2010 Census). The Lipetsk Oblast borders with Ryazan Oblast (NE), Tambov Oblast (E), Voronezh Oblast (S), Kursk Oblast (SW), Oryol Oblast (W), and Tula Oblast (NW). Its location can be viewed by accessing the interactive HealthMap via: http://healthmap.org/r/2mIq. - Mod.CP]

